libhdate-glib
------------------------------------------
LibHdate Gobject bindings

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  cygwin-devel-3.6.9-1
  girepository-GLib2.0-1.86.0-2
  libglib2.0-devel-2.88.1-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.88.1-1
  libhdate-devel-1.6.02-1bl2
  libhdate1-1.6.02-1bl2
  libhdate_glib-devel-0.5.0-1bl1
  libhdate_glib0-0.5.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gobject-introspection-1.86.0-2
  libglib2.0-devel-2.88.1-1
  libhdate-devel-1.6.02-1bl2
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2
  vala-0.56.18-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/yaacov/libhdate-glib

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/yaacov/libhdate-glib/archive/refs/tags/v0.5.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libhdate-glib-0.5.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libhdate-glib-0.5.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libhdate-glib-0.5.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhdate-glib-0.5.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhdate_glib0-0.5.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhdate_glib-devel-0.5.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/girepository-LibHdateGlib1.0-0.5.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/vala-libhdate-glib-0.5.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libhdate-glib)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libhdate-glib.README
  /usr/share/doc/libhdate-glib/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libhdate-glib/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libhdate-glib/README.md

(libhdate_glib0)
  /usr/bin/cyghdate_glib-0.dll

(libhdate_glib-devel)
  /usr/include/hdate-glib.h
  /usr/lib/libhdate_glib.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libhdate-glib.pc

(girepository-LibHdateGlib1.0)
  /usr/lib/girepository-1.0/LibHdateGlib-1.0.typelib
  /usr/share/gir-1.0/LibHdateGlib-1.0.gir

(vala-libhdate-glib)
  /usr/share/vala-0.56/vapi/libhdate-glib.vapi
  /usr/share/vala-0.56/vapi/libhdate.vapi

